        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-11-10T15:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-11-10T15:00:00-05:00" n="1405" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1405">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">393.1115/11–149: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Consul General at Taipei</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Macdonald</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-11-10T15:00:00-05:00">November 10, 1949—3 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>446. In discussing with official personnel question evac their dependents (Deptel
                    423 Nov 2) ConGen, while pointing out that this is of course matter individual
                    decision, shld impress upon them seriousness with which highest qtrs Wash regard
                    safety Amer women and children Formosa, and cite fact that actions such
                    personnel on warning will inevitably tend set example for Amer community.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Webb</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
